Title: New screenshot mode for Multisite
Level: 1
Component: multisite
Compatible: compat
Version: 1.2.5i6
Date: 1414477007
Class: feature

If you add <tt>screenshotmode = True</tt> to your <tt>multisite.mk</tt> or add a <tt>?screenshotmode=1</tt>
to your URL, then Multisite will replace the fancy blue background by a plain white. This makes it easier
to screenshot parts of the GUI like configuration boxes, sidebar snapins, etc.
